                <head>154. Record of a Special Coordination Committee Implementation/Coordination
                    Group Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d154fn1">Source: Carter Library,
                        National Security Council, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss>
                        Institutional Files (H–Files), Box 154. Secret. The meeting took place in
